requests.name: Get Message Docs
requests.description: These message docs provide example messages sent by OBP to the (Kafka) message queue for processing by the Core Banking / Payment system Adapter - together with an example expected response and possible error codes. Integrators can use these messages to build Adapters that provide core banking services to OBP. Note: To enable Kafka connector and this message format, you must set conenctor=kafka_vMar2017 in your Props
